# 詞: 銀包

1. 我個銀包唔見咗，點算呀？ (I can't find my wallet. What should I do?)
2. 佢成日將銀包放喺褲袋，好容易跌出嚟。 (He always keeps his wallet in his pants pocket, so it's very easy to fall out.)
3. 你個銀包幾多錢呀？ (How much money is in your wallet?)
4. 我買咗一個新銀包，好靚仔。 (I bought a new wallet, it looks very handsome.)
5. 小心扒手，佢哋專登搶銀包。 (Beware of pickpockets, they specifically target wallets.)
6. 我個銀包好舊，想換一個新嘅。 (My wallet is very old, I want to replace it with a new one.)
7. 佢將銀包遺留喺餐廳，我哋即刻打俾佢。 (He left his wallet at the restaurant, so we called him immediately.)
8. 你個銀包係皮製定係布製？ (Is your wallet made of leather or cloth?)
9. 我忘記帶銀包，所以無法付款。 (I forgot to bring my wallet, so I couldn't pay.)
10. 佢個銀包好厚，因為裝咗好多信用卡。 (His wallet is very thick because it holds many credit cards.) [end of text]


